ight frontal attack with one key at a time.  It only took two(2)days to crack the file.  No, I don't have any faith in DES.A.G.-- A.G. Russell   Dept A06S  OLTP section of PALS Group   VM ID  SC39093 at AUSVM1Email  arussell@austin.ibm.com       Phone 512-838-7953        TieLine 678-7953These are my views, on anyone else they would look silly. FREE THE BERKELEY 4.4
